ce with it, and to accept it even if you hear it from a child.\u201d I asked, \u201cWhat is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33671,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/fudayl-many-scholars-few-wise\/","url_meta":{"origin":19540,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Hikmah: Many scholars but few who have wisdom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: A man said to Al-Fudayl, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cThe scholars are many.\u201d Al-Fudayl said, \u201cBut those with wisdom are few.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 8\/92 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u0644\u0644\u0641\u0636\u064a\u0644 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u00a0 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0643\u064e\u062b\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064c \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0641\u0636\u064a\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0644 8\/92 \u062d\u0644\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0648\u0644\u064a\u0627\u0621 \u0644\u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38859,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/21\/dua-tyrannical-ruler\/","url_meta":{"origin":19540,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Oppression: Supplication when fearing a tyrannical ruler","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf an imposing ruler comes to you and you fear he will pillage you, then say three times: Allah is the greatest! Allah is more powerful than all His creation together! Allah is mightier than what I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38854,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/21\/companions-muslim-rulers\/","url_meta":{"origin":19540,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sultan: Companions forbid supplicating against Muslim rulers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The eminent among the companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us, saying, \u201cDo not curse your leaders, do not deceive them, and do not hate them. Fear Allah and be patient, for the matter is close at hand.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19540","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com